This package bundles tokenizer data derived from the InternLM official
Hugging Face model repositories:

- internlm/internlm2_5-1_8b
- internlm/internlm2_5-20b

This package also registers the official model alias below against an existing
tokenizer family distributed by another Apache-2.0 package in this monorepo:

- internlm/AlchemistCoder-L-7B -> danube

